Package: sendspin-client
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libportaudio2, libasound2, avahi-daemon
Description: SendSpin Client with enhanced audio features
 This package provides a feature-rich SendSpin client implementation with:
  - Full SendSpin protocol support
  - Enhanced PortAudio integration with device selection
  - ALSA hardware volume control
  - Automatic audio format detection and negotiation
  - mDNS service advertisement for easy discovery
  - Cross-platform support (Linux, macOS, Windows)
 .
 The client supports multiple audio formats including FLAC, OPUS, and PCM,
 and provides both software and hardware volume control options.
